{"pageProps":{"eyebrow":"eunomia-bpf","page":{"layout":"document","title":"ecli server","description":"ecli-server 和 ecli client 子命令已在 2026 年 3 月从主分支移除，以降低维护复杂度。","bodyHtml":"<p><code>ecli-server</code> 和 <code>ecli client</code> 子命令已在 2026 年 3 月从主分支移除，以降低维护复杂度。</p>\n<p>当前发布版本已经不再提供：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>ecli-server</code> 二进制</li>\n<li><code>ecli client</code> 子命令</li>\n<li><code>http</code> only 客户端构建模式</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"现在应该怎么用\">现在应该怎么用</h2>\n<p>当前维护中的工作流是：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>用 <code>ecli run</code> 在本机运行本地包、URL、OCI 镜像或 Wasm 模块</li>\n<li>用 <code>ecli pull</code> 先把 OCI 镜像拉到本地再检查或执行</li>\n<li>用 <code>ecli push</code> 将 Wasm 模块发布到 OCI 仓库</li>\n</ul>\n<p><code>https://eunomia-bpf.github.io/eunomia-bpf/...</code> 下面的历史 GitHub Pages URL 仍然保留给本地 <code>ecli run</code> 兼容使用；这里移除的只是旧的远程 HTTP 控制面。</p>\n<p>示例：</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">wget</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> https://aka.pw/bpf-ecli</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -O</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ecli</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">chmod</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> +x</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./ecli</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./ecli</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> https://eunomia-bpf.github.io/eunomia-bpf/sigsnoop/package.json</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./ecli</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> run</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ghcr.io/eunomia-bpf/execve:latest</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2 id=\"归档实现\">归档实现</h2>\n<p>远程 HTTP 模式最后一版实现保存在主仓库的 <code>archive/ecli-remote-http</code> 分支中：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/tree/archive/ecli-remote-http/ecli\">https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/tree/archive/ecli-remote-http/ecli</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>如果你需要查找历史上的 <code>ecli-server</code>、旧版 OpenAPI 接口或 <code>http</code> only 客户端，请直接看这条归档分支。</p>\n<h2 id=\"给现有用户的说明\">给现有用户的说明</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>仍然提到 <code>ecli-server</code> 的文档或博客，描述的都是历史行为。</li>\n<li>如果你今天仍然需要远程编排，建议把 <code>ecli</code> 放在目标主机上，再在外层使用你自己的 SSH、容器或作业调度方案包装 <code>ecli run</code>。</li>\n</ul>","headings":[{"id":"现在应该怎么用","text":"现在应该怎么用","depth":2},{"id":"归档实现","text":"归档实现","depth":2},{"id":"给现有用户的说明","text":"给现有用户的说明","depth":2}],"sourcePath":"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia.dev/tree/main/docs/eunomia-bpf/ecli/server.zh.md","metadata":{"updatedAt":"2026-03-08T04:58:07.000Z","createdAt":"2026-03-06T07:09:50.000Z","authors":[{"name":"云微","email":"1067852565@qq.com"}]},"path":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/server/","alternates":{"en":"/eunomia-bpf/ecli/server/","zh":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/server/"},"continuation":{"index":{"title":"eunomia-bpf：简化并增强eBPF，支持CO-RE[^1]和WebAssembly[^2]","description":"![GitHub release (latest by date)](https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/releases) ![codecov](https://codecov.io/gh/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf) ![DeepSource](https://deepsource.io/gh/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/?ref=reposi","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/"},"previous":{"title":"ecli","description":"ecli is the local eunomia-bpf CLI for loading, running, pulling, and pushing precompiled programs.","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/"},"next":{"title":"exporter","description":"An prometheus and OpenTelemetry exporter for custom eBPF metrics, written in async rust: eunomia-exporter","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/exporter/"}},"sidebar":[{"title":"eunomia-bpf：简化并增强eBPF，支持CO-RE[^1]和WebAssembly[^2]","items":[{"title":"eunomia-bpf：简化并增强eBPF，支持CO-RE[^1]和WebAssembly[^2]","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/","depth":0},{"title":"Project architecture","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/architecture/","depth":1},{"title":"benchmark","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/benc